3877 #ifndef GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
3878 /* This code block is duplicated in glxext.h, so must be protected */
3879 #define GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
3880 /* Define int32_t, int64_t, and uint64_t types for UST/MSC */
3881 /* (as used in the GL_EXT_timer_query extension). */
3882 #if defined(__STDC_VERSION__) && __STDC_VERSION__ >= 199901L
3883 #include <inttypes.h>
3884 #elif defined(__sun__) || defined(__digital__)
3885 #include <inttypes.h>
3886 #if defined(__STDC__)
3887 #if defined(__arch64__) || defined(_LP64)
3888 typedef long int int64_t;
3889 typedef unsigned long int uint64_t;
3890 #else
3891 typedef long long int int64_t;
3892 typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
3893 #endif /* __arch64__ */
3894 #endif /* __STDC__ */
3895 #elif defined( __VMS ) || defined(__sgi)
3896 #include <inttypes.h>
3897 #elif defined(__SCO__) || defined(__USLC__)
3898 #include <stdint.h>
3899 #elif defined(__UNIXOS2__) || defined(__SOL64__)
3900 typedef long int int32_t;
3901 typedef long long int int64_t;
3902 typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
3903 #elif defined(_WIN32) && defined(__GNUC__)
3904 #include <stdint.h>
3905 #elif defined(_WIN32)
3906 typedef __int32 int32_t;
3907 typedef __int64 int64_t;
3908 typedef unsigned __int64 uint64_t;
3909 #else
3910 #include <inttypes.h> /* Fallback option */
3911 #endif
3912 #endif
3913

3916 typedef uint64_t GLuint64EXT;
